description:
A basic front attack with a push at the end.
Also intrupts target if casting.
name: Attack
note:
<absSettings>
collider: box, 36, 24
infront: true
rotate: true
</absSettings>
<absSequence>
user lock
user pose atk
wait 15
trigger
wait 15
</absSequence>
<absOnDamage>
target cancel
target jump away 24
</absOnDamage>

name: Dodge
note:
Doesn't do much, just moves the user
72 pixels forward at an increased speed

<absSettings>
cooldown: 180
</absSettings>
<absSequence>
user lock
trigger
user speed inc
user move forward 72 true
user speed dec
</absSequence>
